Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 我到底還能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了改變那如狹隘庭園般的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還活不到人生的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗 相擁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在無意識中被刻上的經驗紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當站在懸崖邊的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.47,0:00:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦難抓住了我的手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看到了自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往更加寬廣的領域\N往更深更大的某處
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝著無法預測的世界前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And lt's calling me again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.37,0:16:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,alpha v-4通迅中斷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.45,0:16:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機師無法脫離機體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-1 beta正向RahXephon接近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機師心臟情況異常
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是控制中心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救護班請立即前往373區
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.97,0:01:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.76,0:02:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令，我把他帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼…？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.06,0:02:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎你很意外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功刀司令因為他的管理問題\N受到追究而被免職了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在家裡閉門思過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來你就可以隨意地監禁我或者處決我了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然做出那樣的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你清楚你做的事的嚴重性嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你是不是MU族，我從一開始就討厭你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我是一個公正的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有利用價值我就會利用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.06,0:03:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有那種價值
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，除了能操縱RahXephon…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的人際關係都只是利益關係…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…會好好的利用你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.65,0:03:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了司令官，綾人才剛剛回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不打算服從我的命令的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就請你和前任司令官一樣暫時停職反省一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.34,0:03:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她現在是我的直屬情報分析官
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰啊？那個可愛的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美嶼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識她？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…美嶼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.16,0:04:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,0:04:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，她是新到TERRA來的幹部候補生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，遙少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好，你好像會畫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時間的話我很想看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.14,0:04:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久遠妹妹雖然很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是剛才的女孩也很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這小子！你這種行為是對久遠小姐的背叛！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，她不在了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.86,0:04:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，就那樣失蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！久遠小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳聞說她被財團保護起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,財團啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也聽說那個新司令官是財團的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:04:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是看錯了八雲少佐和紫東小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然圍著那種傢伙團團轉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是徹底的背叛！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們就是那種人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.07,0:05:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我還在停職反省，不是隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.75,0:05:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很意外，你用這種可愛的手帕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你…我可是你的上司
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.17,0:05:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦，現在你不是在停職反省嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,bunga mawar
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.05,0:05:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在隊長祖國的語言中是薔薇的意思吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在這裡的神名綾人就是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了，怎麼了？今天休息？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我申請到了有薪假期
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔父呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人好像已經回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀，真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.36,0:06:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，你也盡心盡力了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護他的人身安全
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很羨慕老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.38,0:07:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對血液的顏色之類的事好像一點也不在意…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣才能像老師你一樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很簡單啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你和我們一起吃次飯就可以了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你就會明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上去準備飯菜收拾浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先在這裡坐一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，你還真的出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被TERRA的人帶出來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來說要讓我住進相關設施裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說好像你住在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就趁他們沒看見的時候跑到這裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是TERRA？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後還發生了這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，不少的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人，可以進來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:07:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.77,0:08:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是MU族這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有介意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…已經不再介意了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是鳥飼守
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是紫東惠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你是從東京…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能對叔父保密嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.06,0:08:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會找機會和他說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時就當成我們倆之間的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們倆的秘密？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.16,0:09:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了，今天我來做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一點像浩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像朝比奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.76,0:09:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這邊也畫畫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個我喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.57,0:09:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想協助神名逃跑的罪責不被追究
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以後就要忠實於我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚能陪我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以退下了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是樹喜歡的人吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是樹喜歡的東西\N你總是想要弄到手…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.56,0:10:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上只有兩種男人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一種能使女人幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.66,0:10:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一種則不能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊，令人厭惡之處和樹一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請轉告總裁，計劃進展順利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.56,0:10:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喝嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上要工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是托了誰的福，現在停職反省…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下子，你是那條白蛇的心腹了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我處世精明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事你都做的出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.05,0:11:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接觸Red
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標確認為D-1
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,point05、mark04、10、blue
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全島進入緊急警戒狀態DEFCON-3
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.58,0:11:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第一級防衛線上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,73區，監視影像切換
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白，放大倍率切換
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對D-1的行動，還未得到許可！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們究竟在幹什麼？ ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.36,0:11:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓alpha小隊出擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.94,0:11:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-1警報發佈、D-1警報發佈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長，你安心地去喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長，這個，我洗乾淨再還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次可以的話，一起去吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.04,0:11:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一點，Donnie
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.47,0:12:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要「鎖定」上司啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Donnie，凱西，我們要為隊長努力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.44,0:12:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標仍然沒有行動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,alpha v，12秒後與敵人接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.26,0:12:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約翰，前面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.05,0:12:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[D-1出現，趕快過來]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時候洗澡真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定知道很多\N不為我所知道的關於綾人的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡風景真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真想讓浩子看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.88,0:13:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很藍…為什麼天空和大海會這麼藍？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.06,0:13:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,alpha v-2嚴重損壞，飛行員已跳傘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-1 beta，來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻象系統開始迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像掉到山裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.27,0:14:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想就這樣死掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人…綾人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你，救救我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的，我很快就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一次，一定！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人！你要去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去駕駛RahXephon
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.67,0:15:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不想再失去任何人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的真好聽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.14,0:15:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳東西！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.86,0:15:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,alpha v-3嚴重損壞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:15:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認奈利亞神殿內的\NRahXephon有自主意識活動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧…正在上升…出來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！快點！開門呀！開門！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.57,0:16:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.87,0:16:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon內有生命反應
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎機師已經就位了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.07,0:17:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,VERMILION
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Donnie
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.96,0:18:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量水平正在無限增長…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.54,0:18:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.96,0:18:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人！請回答
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…想保護…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.06,0:18:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守…大家…大家！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.65,0:18:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底…是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能力水平又上升了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去綾人會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷達反應消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.04,0:19:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有反應，好像已經撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡快確認機師的生存情況
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.67,0:19:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.04,0:19:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還是有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是連這麼點用也派不上…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保護…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓發生在朝比奈身上的一幕再重演了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太慘了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.07,0:19:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，機師怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.94,0:20:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒得救了，頭和腳都不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人啊，廣袤的天空和大海之所以都是藍色的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.14,0:20:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為它們都是屬於藍色血液的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.27,0:21:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一色真說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的人際關係都只是利益關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.78,0:21:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是利益關係也有它自身的美學法則
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.87,0:21:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的幸福就是我的利益
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一點，他還沒有意識到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.88,0:21:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定，他永遠都不會意識到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.34,0:21:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼遙就會孤獨一人…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.27,0:23:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法說出的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.77,0:23:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱藏的語言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.44,0:23:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空，清澄透徹…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.28,0:23:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集，第二十一樂章
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.74,0:23:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Xephon的印記
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.74,0:23:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界飽含著聲音